    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a collector-grade example featuring the robust 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, producing 385 hp and 310 lb-ft of torque. Power is delivered via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis is enhanced by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a 10mm lower ride height, providing exceptional lateral stability and damping precision. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle shows factory-consistent compression and leak-down figures, with a pristine undercarriage and original paint depth verified by gauge. This is a turn-key, high-performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and hydraulic steering feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
