    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable car cover, the exterior boasts a flawless, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirls, stone chips, or door dings. The factory paint retains its original depth and luster. Inside, the cabin is a literal time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and aromatic, with zero creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at certified dealerships with a comprehensive binder of every fluid change and inspection since new. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. With exceptionally low mileage and a pristine history, this vehicle offers a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This is a collector-grade example intended for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
